AEGEAN SEA.
DNC 09.
1. SEISMIC SURVEY 21 MAY THRU 18 JUN BY M/V POLARCUS ALIMA,
   M/V BRAVO SAPPHIRE AND M/V ST JOHN TOWING EIGHT
   5000 METER LONG CABLES IN AREA BOUND BY
   40-56.2N 024-27.2E, 40-50.4N 024-37.7E,
   40-39.0N 024-26.9E, 40-44.8N 024-16.4E.
   FOUR MILE BERTH REQUESTED.
2. CANCEL THIS MSG 19 JUN 15.
